---
title: Carb Smart Sesame Chicken with Stir-Fried Veggies
description: You won't be missing the rice with this recipe! Our Carb Smart Sesame Chicken is jam-packed with all the ingredients you know and love: crisp, flavourful stir-fried veg, spicy umami-rich chicken and a flavour-packed sweet soy sauce that brings it all together!

